data.name: grdMaster.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SPECIMEN_CODE , A.EMERGENCY , A.GUMSA_NAME , RPAD(A.HANGMOG_CODE, 10, '0')|| RPAD(A.SPECIMEN_CODE, 2, '0')|| RPAD(A.EMERGENCY, 1,'0') KEY FROM CPL0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SYSTEM_GUBUN = 'CPL' AND A.HANGMOG_CODE LIKE '%'||:f_hangmog_code||'%' AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE LIKE '%'||:f_specimen_code||'%' AND A.EMERGENCY LIKE '%'||:f_emergency||'%' AND A.GUMSA_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_gumsa_name||'%' ORDER BY KEY

data.name: grdBase.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SPECIMEN_CODE , A.EMERGENCY , A.SEX , A.NAI_FROM , A.NAI_TO , A.FROM_AGE , A.TO_AGE , A.FROM_STANDARD , A.TO_STANDARD , LPAD(A.SEX, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.NAI_FROM, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.NAI_TO, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.FROM_AGE, 10, '0') || LPAD(A.TO_AGE, 10, '0') KEY FROM CPL0104 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE = :f_specimen_code AND A.EMERGENCY = :f_emergency ORDER BY KEY

data.name: grdQryBase.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SPECIMEN_CODE , A.EMERGENCY , A.COMMENTS FROM CPL0103 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE = :f_specimen_code AND A.EMERGENCY = :f_emergency ORDER BY A.COMMENTS

data.name: fwkGesan.InputSQL
data.value: SELECT CODE, CODE_NAME FROM CPL0109 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND ((CODE LIKE '%'||:f_code||'%') OR (CODE_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_code_name||'%')) AND CODE_TYPE = '37' ORDER BY CODE

data.name: grdDelta.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SPECIMEN_CODE , A.EMERGENCY , A.FROM_DELTA_VALUE , A.TO_DELTA_VALUE , A.GESAN , B.CODE_NAME FROM CPL0109 B, CPL0120 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE = :f_specimen_code AND A.EMERGENCY = :f_emergency AND B.CODE_TYPE (+)= '37' AND B.CODE (+)= A.GESAN ORDER BY B.CODE_NAME

data.name: grdPanic.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.SPECIMEN_CODE , A.EMERGENCY , A.SEX , A.NAI_FROM , A.NAI_TO , A.FROM_AGE , A.TO_AGE , A.FROM_VALUE , A.TO_VALUE , LPAD(A.SEX, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.NAI_FROM, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.NAI_TO, 1, '0') || LPAD(A.FROM_AGE, 10, '0') || LPAD(A.TO_AGE, 10, '0') KEY FROM CPL0105 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE = :f_specimen_code AND A.EMERGENCY = :f_emergency ORDER BY KEY
